headline: Tesla, Netflix set to report earnings as US-China trade fight turns 'unsustainable': What to watch this week
summary: As investors enters shutdown week three, a US-China trade war, credit gesticulation, and an incoming oil glut are weighing on the market.

headline: Moody’s (MCO) Valuation in Focus After Analyst Upgrade and Revenue Growth Signals
summary: Raymond James recently moved its outlook on Moody's (MCO) to Market Perform, highlighting the company’s improved issuance activity and reduced valuation risk. Tighter credit spreads have continued to drive revenue within Moody’s dominant ratings business. See our latest analysis for Moody's. This latest analyst upgrade comes as Moody's share price has traded lower recently, with a 1-month share price return of -7.96% and a year-to-date decline of 0.38%.
